      source: 'Reilly PL, Simpson DA, Sprod R, Thomas L. Assessing the conscious level in infants and young children: a paediatric version of the Glasgow Coma Scale. Childs Nerv Syst. 1988;4(1):30-33. (Verbal age-adjustment: James HE. Pediatr Ann. 1986;15(1):16-22.)',
