// spec-v61 §2 A2: related-tool linking. The A2 seed (wells-pe, cockcroft-gault,
// qsofa-sofa) and the v61 inline clusters shipped first; this map finishes the
// rollout so a nurse on a tile is one click from the siblings she actually
// reaches for next. Authored as one reviewable map by clinical family and
// merged into META — identical to an inline `related:` — but the merge defers
// to any `related` already on the tile (the inline v61 entries win), so this
// only fills tiles that have none. Every id is a real, in-catalog tile;
